---
EXERCISE My dynamic Multiple Choice Exercise @ex:myMultiChoice
@code
  let x/y/z/w = rand(10, 20);    % no pair of x, y, z, w is equal
  let c1 = x > w;
  let c2 = y > w;
  let c3 = z > w;
@text
Choose the right answers:
[:c1] $x > w$
[:c2] $y > w$
[:c3] $z > w$
[x]   $1 > 0$    % statically true
[ ]   $1 < 0$    % statically false
