Scoring
=======

---
EXERCISE Scoring example
@options
  scores: 5       % total score of the exercise (5/3 for fa; 10/3 for fb)
@code
  let a = rand(2, 4)
  let b = rand(5, 6)
  let fa = fac(a)
  let fb = fac(b)
@text
Calculate
-) $ a! = $ #fa
-) $ b! = $ #fb
@solution-fb     % if scores are not given for a solution, the
  score: 2       % value 1 is taken.
